PRIVATE_CALENDAR.md

# Privacy-audit pattern source — contains the literal forbidden tokens we
# scan for; must never be in the public repo. Copy from privacy-patterns.example.mjs
# and fill in real patterns. CI gets the file via the PRIVACY_PATTERNS_BASE64
# GitHub Actions secret (decoded at workflow start before pnpm privacy-audit).
scripts/.privacy-patterns.local.mjs

